  <div id="footer_text">Find me on: <%=link_to image_tag("linkedin-logo.png")+" Linkdin", "https://www.linkedin.com/"%> <%=link_to image_tag("github-sign.png")+" GitHub", "https://github.com/reverett4994?tab=repositories"%>  	&nbsp;and <a href="mailto:reverett4994@gmail.com">reverett4994@gmail.com</a></div>
</div>
